Wilfrid Hyde-White https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wilfrid_Hyde-White 0 Wilfrid Hyde-White (12 May 1903 – 6 May 1991) was an English character actor of stage, film and television, who achieved international recognition in his later years for his role as Colonel Pickering in the 1964 film version of the musical My Fair Lady.
